| align="left" | D4A-DEV
| The Defense4All development environment deliverable (D4A-DEV) includes full integration with OpenDaylight toolset (git, bugzilla, etc.)
|- align="left"
| align="left" | D4A-APP
| The Defense4All application deliverable (D4A-APP) includes all the components that run on top of the controller NBAPI. The application will be packaged as a standalone component that interacts with the controller trhough the REST NBAPI. A fully functional detector plugin and a mitigration driver will be included.
|- align="left"
| align="left" | D4A-EXT 
| The Defense4All controller extensions deliverable (D4A-EXT) includes the components that run in the main controller OSGI container, these include the Statistics Collection and the Traffic Redirection services. 
